From the Infowars web site :: On the Friday, July 5 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex breaks down the Egyptian military coup that has driven their first democratically elected president, Mohammed Morsi, out of office. Alex discusses how the people of Egypt came together to oust their Western-backed globalist puppet and overthrow the Muslim Brotherhood in a revolution that has sent the Obama administration reeling. 

Alex also covers the massive police state presence and TSA checkpoints in major towns across the U.S. suppressing the true spirit and meaning of the Fourth of July. 

Financial pundit Max Keiser also joins Alex on today's show to analyze the imploding bond market. 

Alex will also continue to explore the latest NSA spy-gate scandal revelations and other major news items.
